      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A short energy statement from Day 36 of the MONEY program. It works with the specific pattern of tension around a full account: the part that watches the balance waiting for a problem, that can't quite settle into the number being good.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to energy statements? Read ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "how energy statements work",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
